<pb n="0090a" id="I01.0036.0090a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 36</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>安村道俗一百餘人修塔記</title></jhead></juan>
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a01"/><p id="pI01p0090a0101">夫脩心始行。必資願表。表願功能。道由生養。生養之功。謂之塔像。故八塔顯自碧林。
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a02"/>影髮著之香樹。是使見形立善。<note n="0090001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30611;＝範【史】</note><app n="0090001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">範</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30611;</rdg></app>像流今。若非曠積<note n="0090002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30612;＝深【史】</note><app n="0090002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">深</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30612;</rdg></app>因。慈悲宿造。則必弱<note n="0090003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB07656;＝喪【史】</note><app n="0090003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">喪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB07656;</rdg></app>忘歸。
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a03"/>長迷誰覺。唯雅見君子能改<note n="0090004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30613;＝步【史】</note><app n="0090004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">步</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30613;</rdg></app>迷方。控平軒於一乘。移心弱<app source="0090003" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">喪</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB07656;</rdg></app>。汎神舟於三路。是以
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a04"/>獲<note n="0090005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30614;＝嘉【史】</note><app n="0090005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">嘉</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30614;</rdg></app>縣東。清流福地。號曰安村。有大檀主。　　　置立尼寺。有故天宮一區。<note n="0090006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30618;＝年【史】</note><app n="0090006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">年</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30618;</rdg></app>久事
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a05"/>遐。神功頓毀。寶色莊嚴。散靈像於輕塵。陵雲雅<note n="0090007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30615;＝製【史】</note><app n="0090007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">製</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30615;</rdg></app>。落真儀於重壤。玉地<app source="0090002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">深</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30612;</rdg></app>經。&CI0003;若
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a06"/>存。寶相祇林。神容中斷。乃復道俗一百餘人。發悟自心。輕財重道。捨身命財。共脩故
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a07"/>塔。始末十旬。微功乃就。復妙相於靈山。<note n="0090008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30616;＝還【史】</note><app n="0090008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">還</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30616;</rdg></app>湛一於雙樹。義感去來。精貫<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">現</unclear>在。邈<note n="0090009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30617;＝象【史】</note><app n="0090009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">象</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30617;</rdg></app>護
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a08"/>於金經。超名敕於玉牒。釋梵來儀。乘碧霧以通煙。四王效像。曜五花於日月。淨水香
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a09"/>雲。若<note n="0090010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB18853;＝離【史】</note><app n="0090010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">離</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB18853;</rdg></app>復合。異物芬芳。殊方琣b。金剛豈遠。此地長春。十種莊嚴。事同紫岸。因茲業
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a10"/>也。一百人等。發斯洪願。願令　皇家。寶運<app source="0090002" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">深</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30612;</rdg></app>基。道契二儀之堅。玉蒂金根。福同九山
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a11"/>之宅。異物諍祥。雲華帝門。奇&CB30664;競像。風翻上國。破四魔於五雲。拔三鋒於四濘。甘露
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a12"/>淨音。導一乘於方方。法水金開。灌千迷於莫〃。三有一歸。同軒佛寶。哀鸞和雅。調八
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a13"/>梵於清蓮。冥讚空絃。妙龍舟於幽俗。往聖所以懸苻。來賢所以共一。思報四恩。常脩
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a14"/>□度。火劍自消。三途永息。莫不盡化<app source="0090008" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">還</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30616;</rdg></app>&CB07099;。妙鄰二智。滅諦夷然。誰非佛者。奉慈氏於
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a15"/>初覺。會千佛於淨<app source="0090006" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">年</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30618;</rdg></app>。正心正見。唯願如是。
<lb ed="C I" n="0090a16"/>　　　　　　　　　　唯大魏天平四<app source="0090006" type="＊"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">年</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30618;</rdg></app>歲次丁巳七月甲午朔廿五日戊午</p>
